Preprocessing

seurat<-c("WT", "KO") %>%
  setNames(.,.) %>% 
  lapply(function(x){
    Read10X_h5(sprintf("%s_filtered_feature_bc_matrix.h5",x)) %>% 
      `rownames<-`(MT.name(rownames(.))) %>% 
      `colnames<-`(paste0(x,"_",colnames(.)))
  })  %>% 
  Reduce(Matrix::cbind2, .) 

seurat<-CreateSeuratObject(counts=seurat,min.cells=0,min.features = 0)
seurat@meta.data$genotype<-colnames(seurat@assays$RNA@counts) %>% 
  sapply(function(x){
    strsplit(x,split="_[ATGC][ATGC]")[[1]][1] %>%
      factor(., levels =c("WT", "KO"))
  })

table(seurat@meta.data$genotype)
## 
##   WT   KO 
## 8369 8021
seurat[["percent.mito"]]<-PercentageFeatureSet(seurat,pattern="^MT-")

meta.data<-seurat@meta.data
meta.data$bad<-rep(0,nrow(meta.data))
meta.data$bad[meta.data$nFeature_RNA<ngene_low|ngene_high<meta.data$nFeature_RNA]<-1
meta.data$bad[meta.data$nCount_RNA<numi_low|numi_high<meta.data$nCount_RNA]<-1
meta.data$bad[meta.data$percent.mito<mito_low|meta.data$percent.mito>mito_high]<-1
meta.data$bad<-factor(meta.data$bad)


kable(table(ifelse(meta.data$bad==0,"High quality","Law quality"),meta.data$genotype))

# Finally here filter data with odd features
seurat<-subset(seurat,subset=nFeature_RNA>ngene_low & nFeature_RNA<ngene_high &percent.mito<mito_high & nCount_RNA>numi_low & nCount_RNA<numi_high)

Doublet removal

# Read doublet status
# add multiplet status
seurat@meta.data$pred_State<-levels(seurat@meta.data$genotype) %>%
  lapply(function(x){
    file<-intersect(dir(path="./2_doublets",pattern=x,full.names = TRUE),
                    dir(path="./2_doublets",pattern="predicted_doublets",full.names = TRUE))     
    fread(file) %>%
      unlist()
  }) %>% unlist()
seurat@meta.data$pred_State<-ifelse(seurat@meta.data$pred_State==TRUE,"multiplet","singlet")

seurat@meta.data$doublet_scores<-levels(seurat@meta.data$genotype) %>% 
  lapply(function(x){
    file<-intersect(dir(path="./2_doublets",pattern=x,full.names = TRUE),
                    dir(path="./2_doublets",pattern="scores",full.names = TRUE))     
    fread(file) %>%
      unlist()
  }) %>% unlist()

seurat <- NormalizeData(seurat, normalization.method = "LogNormalize", scale.factor = 10000)
seurat <- FindVariableFeatures(seurat, selection.method = "vst", nfeatures = 2000)
all.genes <- rownames(seurat)

seurat <- RunPCA(seurat, features = VariableFeatures(object = seurat))

Call DEGs in each cell types

DEG_analysis <- function(trg){
  dat<-seurat[["umap"]][[]] %>% as.data.frame()
dat<-cbind(dat,seurat@meta.data)
dat$celltype<-ifelse(dat$celltype%in% trg,"cell type of interest","others") %>% 
  factor(levels=c("cell type of interest","others"))
plts<-levels(dat$celltype) %>%
  lapply(function(x){
    ggplot(NULL)+
      geom_point(dat,mapping=aes(x=UMAP_1,y=UMAP_2),color="grey",size=0.1)+
      geom_point(dplyr::filter(dat,celltype==x),mapping=aes(x=UMAP_1,y=UMAP_2),color="red",size=0.1)+
      ggtitle(x)
  })
grid.arrange(grobs = plts, ncol = 2)

trg.seurat<-subset(seurat, subset=celltype%in%trg)

Idents(trg.seurat) <- trg.seurat@meta.data$genotype


cluster.markers <- FindMarkers(trg.seurat, ident.1 = "KO", min.pct = 0.25)
datatable(cluster.markers)
}
